A sliding Christmas tree light mounting assembly is provided including a house having a fascia. A string of lights include an elongated flexible insulated wire with multiple light bulbs spaced along a length thereof and electrically connected to the same for receiving power therefrom. At least one elongated linear slider track is included. A plurality of slider clips are slidably coupled to the slider track and adapted to releasably secure to the string of lights for mounting the same to the fascia.